{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<mroot>","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mroot","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","hasMathML":true,"sidebarHTML":"\n    <ol>\n        <li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element\">MathML Reference</a></strong>\n\n        \n            </li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/maction\">&lt;maction&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\">&lt;math&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/menclose\">&lt;menclose&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/merror\">&lt;merror&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfenced\">&lt;mfenced&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac\">&lt;mfrac&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mi\">&lt;mi&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mmultiscripts\">&lt;mmultiscripts&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mn\">&lt;mn&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mover\">&lt;mover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\">&lt;mpadded&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mphantom\">&lt;mphantom&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mroot\">&lt;mroot&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mrow\">&lt;mrow&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\">&lt;ms&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msqrt\">&lt;msqrt&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\">&lt;mstyle&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msub\">&lt;msub&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msubsup\">&lt;msubsup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msup\">&lt;msup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\">&lt;mtd&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtext\">&lt;mtext&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtr\">&lt;mtr&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munder\">&lt;munder&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munderover\">&lt;munderover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/semantics\">&lt;semantics&gt;</a></li>\n        \n\n        \n    </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p class=\"summary\">MathML の <code>&lt;mroot&gt;</code> 要素は根指数の付いた累乗根を表示するのに用いられます。引数は二つあり，構文は <code>&lt;mroot&gt; <em>基数 根指数</em> &lt;/mroot&gt;</code> となります。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attributes","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"attr-class-id-style\">class, id, style</dt>\n <dd><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS\">スタイルシート</a>で使用するために使います。</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-displaystyle\"><code>displaystyle</code></dt>\n <dd>論理値で、数式を表示する際に上下に余白を追加するかどうかを指定します。 <code>false</code> に設定すると、数式を表示するのによりコンパクトなレイアウトを使用します。 <code>displaystyle</code> を <code>true</code> に設定する主な効果は、演算子をより大きく表示することです。 <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code> の <code>largeop</code> および <code>movablelimits</code> も参照してください。</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-href\">href</dt>\n <dd>指定された URL へのハイパーリンクを設定するために使われます。</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-mathbackground\">mathbackground</dt>\n <dd>背景色を指定します。 <code>#rgb</code> や <code>#rrggbb</code> のような16進表現や<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/color_value#color_keywords\">HTML 色名</a>を用いることができます</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-mathcolor\">mathcolor</dt>\n <dd>文字や記号自体の色を指定します。 <code>#rgb</code> や <code>#rrggbb</code> のような16進表現や <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/color_value#color_keywords\">HTML color 色名</a>を用いることができます</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>レンダリングのサンプル(画像): <img alt=\"x\" src=\"/files/3200/mroot.png\" style=\"margin-left: 10px; vertical-align: middle;\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n\n<p>ブラウザのレンダリング結果: <math> <mroot> <mi>x</mi> <mn>3</mn> </mroot> </math></p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mroot</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>x<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>3<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mroot</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://mathml-refresh.github.io/mathml-core/#radicals-msqrt-mroot\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathML Core<br><small lang=\"ja\">mroot の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-draft\">ドラフト</span></td>\n   <td>草稿の仕様</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML3/chapter3.html#presm.mroot\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathML 3.0<br><small lang=\"ja\">mroot の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">勧告</span></td>\n   <td>現在の仕様</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML2/chapter3.html#presm.mroot\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathML 2.0<br><small lang=\"ja\">mroot の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">勧告</span></td>\n   <td>初回定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"mathml.elements.mroot","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mroot/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msqrt\" title=\"<msqrt>\">&lt;msqrt&gt;</a></code> (根指数のない平方根)</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"attributes"},{"text":"例","id":"examples"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"MathML の <mroot> 要素は根指数の付いた累乗根を表示するのに用いられます。引数は二つあり，構文は <mroot> 基数 根指数 </mroot> となります。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<mroot>","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"<mroot>","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<mroot>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/mathml/element/mroot","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/mathml/element/mroot/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML","title":"MathML"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element","title":"MathML 要素リファレンス"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mroot","title":"<mroot>"}],"pageTitle":"<mroot> - MathML | MDN","noIndexing":false}}